'''Sparkbees''' were creatures used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Originally a type of bee native to [[Yuuzhan'tar]], sparkbees were used as the templates for the projectile biots that became the [[Nang hul|Thud]], [[Razor bug|Razor]], [[Snap bug|Snap]], and [[Blast bug]]s. Sparkbees were also kept in their un-shaped form as well, as [[Sparkbee honey|their honey]] was considered a delicacy. However, their populations were heavily controlled, as the honey was flammable, and was especially dangerous to [[Vonduun Skerr Kyrric|Vonduun crab armor]].

